-lived transients, but ultimately abruptly transition to one of the stable\nperiodic states identified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 May 2021 17:30:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Jul 2021 20:44:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 03:53:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-17"}
