rameters, radiation\npatterns, beamforming capabilities, and enhanced gain are all verified by\nmeasurements over the operating bandwidth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 May 2021 18:00:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 21:05:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-24"}
